name: New York City
description:
The ghosts promise to each other that they'll adventure to the place where they couldn't go when they're still alive. For me, Death is like freedom, 
No one knows what life after death looks like, but if I could, I'd go somewhere I couldn't have gone when I was alive. I decided to use ghost characters because I want to convey that everyone—whatever gender you are, how old you are can has freedom.
